trans-unit.source: Provides parsing support for <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.List" /> and <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.SelectionList" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte de análise para controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.List" /> e <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.SelectionList" />.

trans-unit.source: For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/aspnet/mobile/overview">Mobile Apps & Sites with ASP.NET</see>.
trans-unit.target: Para saber mais sobre como desenvolver aplicativos móveis ASP.NET, confira <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/aspnet/mobile/overview">Aplicativos Móveis & Sites com ASP.NET</see>.

trans-unit.source: This class is created internally and used by the page parser when parsing a `<mobile:List>` or `<mobile:SelectionList>` tag.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é criada internamente e usada pelo analisador de página durante a análise de um `<mobile:List>` ou `<mobile:SelectionList>` marca.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ListControlBuilder> class recognizes statically declared <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.MobileListItem> elements.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ListControlBuilder> classe reconhece declarada estaticamente <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.MobileListItem> elementos.

trans-unit.source: for operating in a hosted environment.
trans-unit.target: para operação em um ambiente hospedado.
